{"tid":2074984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【博爾頓新書】習當面訓特朗普：中國不簽不平等條約　暗示反美","createTime":"2020-06-22T13:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T01:53:27.000Z","uid":304281,"like":131,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"06bc049fca8802b9716e36bdd0061cde4744942a","tid":2074984,"uid":304281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:37:33.000Z","msg":"聽到特朗普的提議後，習近平突然表示，中美雙方若談成「不平等」的貿易協議，中國受到的「屈辱」會如同當年中國在一次大戰後「凡爾賽和約」那樣，山東省從德國手中被轉讓給日本。<br />\n<br />\n【中美角力】特朗普為連任向習近平求情？博爾頓新書投「政治震撼彈」<br />\n<br />\n【中美角力】博爾頓揭特朗普冷待香港議題：我們都有人權問題<br />\n<br />\n習近平板著臉回答，若中國在貿易談判受到同樣屈辱，國內愛國情緒將高漲，暗示人民會反美。<br />\n<br />\n博爾頓說，特朗普顯然不知道習近平在說什麼，但特朗普對於歷史很能發揮。特朗普暗示，美國在二次大戰幫助中國擊敗日本，中方欠美國一個人情。<br />\n<br />\n習近平接著開始「訓話」，表示中國當時奮戰19年，而且主要是靠自己擊敗日本侵略。博爾頓在書中宣稱，雖然中共當時多數時間都在迴避日軍，並試圖暗中破壞國民政府。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2676411/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2676411%2F&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=fb7fc7b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2676411/</a><br />\n<br />\n有無人明個小學雞講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab2c35bab53cba33f0ada1846f7a24215f79aac","tid":2074984,"uid":132587,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:38:18.000Z","msg":"我淨係知佢一路幫我地助攻"},{"pid":"5c5fc7f4be3483e6a16cc013511356195bca3c5a","tid":2074984,"uid":149494,"like":11,"dislike":28,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:38:51.000Z","msg":"特朗普真係無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354822639b94046ba7d425b89551177513526229","tid":2074984,"uid":32220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:39:56.000Z","msg":"第一階段貿易協定係公平既咩？"},{"pid":"6ac6927c32e7eb10cbf9794835f7acd1ef3e98c5","tid":2074984,"uid":304281,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:40:44.000Z","msg":"山東問題是指第一次世界大戰期間，日本藉口對德國宣戰，出兵中國山東，而產生的領土主權爭議。在戰後的巴黎和會上，中華民國作為一戰的戰勝國，卻被日本政府要求把戰敗國德國在山東的權益轉交予日本而非歸還中國。由於中華民國北洋政府未能維護國家領土和主權的完整，從而直接引發了1919年的五四運動，對近代中國產生了巨大的影響[1]。山東問題直到1922年華盛頓會議才<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">在美國的調停下得以解決</span></strong></span>。[2]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%B1%E6%9D%B1%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=28cd8a25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%B1%E6%9D%B1%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4884c0687df1ab3d92d2aceea32b6f38630ca2a","tid":2074984,"uid":30067,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:29:54.000Z","msg":"當年就唔應該俾中國人自己管<br />\n外國管中國人100年 d中國人先會正常返d"},{"pid":"19a3208dad95191ef56f3ad3725ee12a73f9d688","tid":2074984,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"354822639b94046ba7d425b89551177513526229","tid":2074984,"uid":32220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:39:56.000Z","msg":"第一階段貿易協定係公平既咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:31:58.000Z","msg":"口交下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1745b864f5bdac1cceddce9195c28f8e1e5a57b","tid":2074984,"uid":39777,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"原來依家中國人唔係反美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{